<p>Maine offers additional state-level incentives, including sales tax exemptions on solar equipment and property tax exemptions on the added home value from solar installations. The state's net metering program through CMP allows solar customers to receive full retail credit for excess electricity fed back to the grid, essentially using the grid as a battery system. Efficiency Maine provides rebates for high-efficiency heat pumps, with cold-climate air-source heat pumps eligible for rebates up to \$2,000 per system.</p>

